{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880963431,"sessionID":"ses_28540a122ffeV6GyViz90QWuux","part":{"id":"prt_d7abf6b5f0013OCfvYMQmS9b1p","messageID":"msg_d7abf5fd2001n9x3Y2yi0Z5jOC","sessionID":"ses_28540a122ffeV6GyViz90QWuux","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"toolu_f9cfa44bfa82430eae70278c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project to understand its structure. I need to verify implementation against spec AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding).\n\nFind:\n1. The project root and main directory structure\n2. Any manifest files related to RBAC (ServiceAccount, Role, RoleBinding, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding)\n3. Any spec or requirements documents for AR-031\n4. Test files related to RBAC or manifests\n\nSearch thoroughly in directories like manifests/, config/, k8s/, helm/, or similar. Return file paths and a summary of what you find.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_285408834ffewM3KgBPtmUSYzC (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the agentcube project's AR-031 RBAC implementation. Here is my detailed summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-031 RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) - Implementation Summary\n\n### 1. Project Root and Main Directory Structure\n\n**Project Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z`\n\n**Key Directories:**\n```\nagentcube/\n├── manifests/                          # RBAC manifests and Helm charts\n│   ├── charts/base/                    # Main Helm chart\n│   │   ├── templates/\n│   │   │   ├── rbac/\n│   │   │   │   └── workloadmanager.yaml    # WorkloadManager RBAC\n│   │   │   ├── rbac-router.yaml            # Router RBAC (optional)\n│   │   │   └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\n│   │   ├── tests/                        # Helm unit tests\n│   │   ├── crds/                         # Custom Resource Definitions\n│   │   ├── values.yaml\n│   │   └── Chart.yaml\n│   ├── design.md                         # Helm chart design doc\n│   └── delta-spec.md                     # Delta specification\n├── changes/AR-031/                       # AR-031 implementation folder\n│   ├── proposal.md                       # Full AR-031 proposal (Chinese)\n│   ├── tasks.md                          # Detailed task checklist\n│   ├── status.json\n│   └── README.md\n├── sandbox-orchestration/AR-031-rbac-config/\n│   └── design.md                         # Standalone RBAC design doc\n└── [other project dirs: pkg/, cmd/, sdk-python/, etc.]\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. RBAC Manifest Files Found\n\n#### WorkloadManager RBAC (Always Installed)\n| File | Path | Type |\n|------|------|------|\n| **ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | Combined YAML |\n\n**Resources Defined:**\n- `ServiceAccount/workloadmanager` (namespace-scoped)\n- `ClusterRole/workloadmanager` (cluster-wide permissions for sandboxes, codeinterpreters, agentruntimes, secrets, tokenreviews)\n- `ClusterRoleBinding/workloadmanager` (binds SA to ClusterRole)\n\n#### Router RBAC (Optional, disabled by default)\n| File | Path | Type |\n|------|------|------|\n| **ServiceAccount, Role, RoleBinding** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Conditional YAML |\n\n**Controlled by:** `router.rbac.create` (default: `false`)  \n**Configurable SA name:** `router.serviceAccountName` (default: `agentcube-router`)\n\n#### Volcano Agent Scheduler RBAC (Optional, disabled by default)\n| File | Path | Type |\n|------|------|------|\n| **ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T1