no Scheduler Tests** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/tests/volcano-scheduler_test.yaml` | Tests Volcano RBAC conditional rendering and bindings |\n\n**Test Framework:** Helm unittest (using `helm unittest` plugin)\n\n---\n\n### 5. Key RBAC Specifications Summary\n\n#### WorkloadManager ClusterRole Permissions:\n| API Group | Resources | Verbs |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|\n| `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxclaims`, `sandboxtemplates`, `sandboxwarmpools` | get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete |\n| `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools/status` | get, update, patch |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters` | get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/status` | get, update, patch |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/finalizers` | update |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes` | get, list, watch |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes/status` | update, patch |\n| `` (core) | `pods` | get, list, watch |\n| `authentication.k8s.io` | `tokenreviews` | create |\n| `` (core) | `secrets` | get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete |\n\n#### Router Role Permissions (namespace-scoped):\n| API Group | Resources | Verbs |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|\n| `` (core) | `secrets` | get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete |\n\n#### Volcano ClusterRole Permissions:\nComprehensive scheduling permissions including: pods, nodes, namespaces, services, PVCs, PVs, CRDs, podgroups, leases, resourceclaims, etc.\n\n---\n\n### 6. Configuration Values (values.yaml)\n\n```yaml\nrouter:\n  serviceAccountName: \"\"       # Empty = default \"agentcube-router\"\n  rbac:\n    create: false              # Disabled by default\n\nvolcano:\n  scheduler:\n    enabled: false             # Disabled by default\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. Implementation Status\n\nBased on `tasks.md`, the implementation is marked as **Stage ST-3 (completed)** with all 20 acceptance criteria marked as complete:\n- WorkloadManager RBAC: Fully implemented\n- Router RBAC: Optional, properly guarded\n- Volcano RBAC: Optional, properly guarded\n- Tests: All helm unittest files present\n- Documentation: Proposal, tasks, and design docs complete\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_285408834ffewM3KgBPtmUSYzC","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.5-plus","providerID":"bailian-coding-plan"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775880861640,"end":1775880963428}}}}
