{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880981293,"sessionID":"ses_28540a122ffeV6GyViz90QWuux","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac14506001x4ANGztWIfxRvc","messageID":"msg_d7ac12716001vs2qMuUL1x9oeH","sessionID":"ses_28540a122ffeV6GyViz90QWuux","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_7976bb41cbe84746aa50eb9c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/tests/volcano-scheduler_test.yaml"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/tests/volcano-scheduler_test.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: suite: Volcano Scheduler Tests\n2: templates:\n3:   - volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\n4: tests:\n5:   - it: should not render Volcano scheduler resources when disabled\n6:     set:\n7:       volcano:\n8:         scheduler:\n9:           enabled: false\n10:     asserts:\n11:       - hasDocuments:\n12:           count: 0\n13: \n14:   - it: should render all Volcano scheduler resources when enabled\n15:     set:\n16:       volcano:\n17:         scheduler:\n18:           enabled: true\n19:     asserts:\n20:       - hasDocuments:\n21:           count: 6\n22:       - isKind:\n23:           of: ServiceAccount\n24:         documentIndex: 0\n25:       - isKind:\n26:           of: ConfigMap\n27:         documentIndex: 1\n28:       - isKind:\n29:           of: ClusterRole\n30:         documentIndex: 2\n31:       - isKind:\n32:           of: ClusterRoleBinding\n33:         documentIndex: 3\n34:       - isKind:\n35:           of: Service\n36:         documentIndex: 4\n37:       - isKind:\n38:           of: Deployment\n39:         documentIndex: 5\n40: \n41:   - it: should render with default replicas\n42:     set:\n43:       volcano:\n44:         scheduler:\n45:           enabled: true\n46:     asserts:\n47:       - equal:\n48:           path: spec.replicas\n49:           value: 1\n50:         documentIndex: 5\n51: \n52:   - it: should render with custom replicas\n53:     set:\n54:       volcano:\n55:         scheduler:\n56:           enabled: true\n57:           replicas: 3\n58:     asserts:\n59:       - equal:\n60:           path: spec.replicas\n61:           value: 3\n62:         documentIndex: 5\n63: \n64:   - it: should render with custom image\n65:     set:\n66:       volcano:\n67:         scheduler:\n68:           enabled: true\n69:           image:\n70:             repository: custom/vc-agent-scheduler\n71:             tag: v1.0.0\n72:     asserts:\n73:       - equal:\n74:           path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].image\n75:           value: custom/vc-agent-scheduler:v1.0.0\n76:         documentIndex: 5\n77: \n78:   - it: should have correct ConfigMap data\n79:     set:\n80:       volcano:\n81:         scheduler:\n82:           enabled: true\n83:     asserts:\n84:       - equal:\n85:           path: metadata.name\n86:           value: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n87:         documentIndex: 1\n88:       - isNotNull:\n89:           path: data.agent-scheduler.conf\n90:         documentIndex: 1\n91: \n92:   - it: should have prometheus annotations on service\n93:     set:\n94:       volcano:\n95:         scheduler:\n96:           enabled: true\n97:     asserts:\n98:       - equal:\n99:           path: metadata.annotations.prometheus\\.io/scrape\n100:           value: \"true\"\n101:         documentIndex: 4\n102:       - equal:\n103:           path: metadata.annotations.prometheus\\.io/port\n104:           value: \"8080\"\n105:         documentIndex: 4\n106:       - equal:\n107:           path: spec.ports[0].port\n108:           value: 8080\n109:         documentIndex: 4\n110: \n111:   - it: should have correct ClusterRoleBinding subject\n112:     set:\n113:       volcano:\n114:         scheduler:\n115:           enabled: true\n116:     asserts:\n117:       - equal:\n118:           path: roleRef.kind\n119:           value: ClusterRole\n120:         documentIndex: 3\n121:       - equal:\n122:           path: roleRef.name\n123:           value: volcano-agent-scheduler\n124:         documentIndex: 3\n125:       - equal:\n126:           path: subjects[0].kind\n127:           value: ServiceAccount\n128:         documentIndex: 3\n129:       - equal:\n130:           path: subjects[0].name\n131:           value: volcano-agent-scheduler\n132:         documentIndex: 3\n133: \n134:   - it: should mount config volume and tmp volume\n135:     set:\n136:       volcano:\n137:         scheduler:\n138:           enabled: true\n139:     asserts:\n140:       - equal:\n141:           path: spec.template.spec.volumes[0].name\n142:           value: config-volume\n143:         documentIndex: 5\n144:       - equal:\n145:           path: spec.template.spec.volumes[0].configMap.name\n146:           value: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n147:         documentIndex: 5\n148:       - equal:\n149:           path: spec.template.spec.volumes[1].name\n150:           value: tmp-volume\n151:         documentIndex: 5\n152:       - isNotNull:\n153:           path: spec.template.spec.volumes[1].emptyDir\n154:         documentIndex: 5\n\n(End of file - total 154 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"suite: Volcano Scheduler Tests\ntemplates:\n  - volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\ntests:\n  - it: should not render Volcano scheduler resources when disabled\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: false\n    asserts:\n      - hasDocuments:\n          count: 0\n\n  - it: should render all Volcano scheduler resources when enabled\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n    asserts:\n      - hasDocuments:","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/tests/volcano-scheduler_test.yaml","time":{"start":1775880981275,"end":1775880981291}}}}
